examples.text: Kazadan sonra kalbi durunca defibrilatör bir süre attırdı.
examples.translation: When [his/her/its] heart stopped beating after the crash, the defibrillator made it beating for a time.
After this, they found somebody to threw the man suck him. (literally and colloquially: "...to throw him out.")

etymology: Inherited from Ottoman Turkish آتدیرمق (attırmak). Intrusive form of atmak.
